2019/02/bond-25-moves-back-two-months-in-2020-1202558710/|title=\u2018Bond 25\u2019 Looks To Shake Up Easter 2020|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|date=2019-02-15|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2019-02-16}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Samaritan''\n| December 11, 2020\n| co-production with [[Sylvester Stallone|Balboa Productions]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"4\" | 2021\n| ''[[Cash Truck (upcoming film)|Cash Truck]]''\n|  January 15, 2021<ref>https://deadline.com/2020/03/jason-statham-exits-man-from-toronto-kevin-hart-sony-pictures-1202873741/</ref>\n| co-production with [[Miramax]] and Ritchie/Wigram Productions\n|-\n| ''Dog''\n|  February 14, 2021\n| co-production with [[Channing Tatum|Free Association]]<ref>https://variety.com/2020/film/news/channing-tatum-dog-movie-mgm-1203521279/</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Tomb Raider (2018 film)#Future|Tomb Raider 2]]''\n| March 19, 2021\n| co-production with [[GK Films]] and [[Square Enix]]\n|-\n| ''[[The Addams Family (2019 film)#Sequel|The Addams Family 2]]''\n| October 22, 2021\n| co-production with [[Bron Studios|Bron Creative]], The Jackal Group, [[Whalerock Industries]], and [[Cinesite|Cinesite Studios]];<ref name=\"Deadline\"/> U.S. Distribution only; international distribution by [[Universal Pictures]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"1\" | 2022\n| Untitled ''[[Sesame Street]]'' musical\n| January 22, 2022<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/shazam-2-to-take-flight-spring-2022-sesame-street-relocates-1202807958/|title=\u2018Shazam! 2\u2019 To Take Flight Spring 2022, \u2018Sesame Street\u2019 Relocates|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|date=2019-12-12|website=Deadline|language=en|access-date=2019-12-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title='Sesame Street' Movie Taps 'Portlandia' Co-Creator Jonathan Krisel as Director (EXCLUSIVE)|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/sesame-street-movie-director-jonathan-krisel-portlandia-1202961279/|accessdate=February 21, 2019|work=Variety|